<div class="textcontent">
<strong>The Milford Club </strong><br>
<i>“It’s more than just a room”</i>

<p>The Milford Club is an exclusive program designed to meet the needs of the discriminating traveler who appreciate convenience, comfort, service, and a loyalty program with special benefits.</p>

<strong>Milford Club amenities and services include:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Upgraded accommodations to our Milford Club guest rooms</li>
<li>Free High Speed Internet Access</li>
<li>Free local and toll free phone calls, and direct phone line</li>
<li>Dedicated Milford Club reservations agent and dedicated check-in</li>
<li>Complimentary continental breakfast in our exclusive Milford Club Lounge</li>
<li>Complimentary morning newspaper available in the Milford Club lounge</li>
<li>Personalized concierge service in the Milford Club Lounge</li>
<li>Loyalty Program with special benefits</li>
</ul>

<p>To book the Milford Club, please <a href="https://booker.hotelfactory.com/cgi/uzbook1.cgi?p=5680&c=UZ&s=MLF5680&r=www.milfordplaza.com&cid=mcp" target="_blank" class="textlink">click here</a></p><br>
